<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>Fix for <link linkend="_namespace_c_g_a_l">CGAL</link> bugs in polygon with holes verification Contained in <link linkend="_namespace_c_g_a_l">CGAL</link> PR #3688, likely to be in 4.14 version of <link linkend="_namespace_c_g_a_l">CGAL</link>. </para>

<para>Modified for Pepr3D to prevent flipping of camera.</para>

<para>For now, just keep this custom patched include file first, to avoid using <link linkend="_namespace_c_g_a_l">CGAL</link>&apos;s version </para>
</section>
